"{\"uid\": \"cbsnews.com-news-paris-olympics-2024-breaker-refugee-afghan\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Watch CBS News  August 10, 2024 / 10:40 AM EDT/ AP  Refugee breaker Manizha Talash, or \\\"b-girl Talash,\\\" was disqualified from thefirst everOlympicbreaking competitionon Friday after she wore a cape that said \\\"Free Afghan Women\\\" during her pre-qualifier battle against India Sardjoe - known as \\\"b-girl India.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9999444257316403, \"rank\": 5.557673521790309e-05, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}, {\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.6633238572158519, \"rank\": 0.3736984447934731, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old, originally fromAfghanistanand representing theOlympic Refugee Team, lost in thepre-qualifier battleagainst Sardjoe and would not have advanced even if she had not been disqualified.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Refugee Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Political statements and slogansare banned on the field of play and on podiums at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"World DanceSport Federation, the governing body forbreakingat the Olympics, issued a statement afterward that said she \\\"was disqualified for displaying a political slogan on her attire during the Pre-Qualifier battle.\\\"\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 606, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World DanceSport Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Talash sought asylum in Spain afterfleeing Taliban rulein her home country in 2021.\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 850, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6113916741084201, \"rank\": 0.5415874874461254, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 869, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Taliban_offensive\", \"score\": 0.7356178922334778, \"rank\": 0.3477708877721168, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Taliban_offensive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Taliban_offensive\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am here because I want to reach my dream.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not because I am scared,\\\" she told The Associated Press before the Olympics from Spain, where she was granted asylum.\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999943762089853, \"rank\": 5.623733418005346e-06, \"text\": \"Associated Press\",